UserDashboard.tsx`. I am focusing on improving user interaction and ensuring data flow.\n\n\n**Implementing Workout Plan**\n\nI\'m now integrating workout plans and check-in features within the UI and implementing coach chat in `UserDashboard.tsx`. I\'m optimizing UI elements to improve user experience. The primary focus is on refining the user interface and streamlining the data flow.\n\n\n**Overhauling UI Components**\n\nI\'m now overhauling and consolidating the components within `UserDashboard.tsx`, simplifying the layout. I am ensuring smooth data flow and implementing new UI elements for profile setup. I\'m focusing on consistency.\n\n\n\n"
