  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Considering File Edit Call**\n\nI\'m now focusing on preparing the `multi_edit_file` call, starting with the necessary imports for React components and associated utility functions. I\'ve got the initial set of imports needed, including `useState` and various icon components, and I\'m currently working on structuring how the data will be passed to this function.\n\n\n**Structuring State & Generation**\n\nI\'m now implementing the React state variables for the user dashboard. I\'ve set up `activeTab`, `isSidebarOpen`, the `profile` object, and the `dietPlan` state. Additionally, I\'ve defined `isGenerating` and `error` states to manage the loading state and potential errors during the plan generation. The plan generation function is next on the list.\n\n\n**Defining Plan Generation Call**\n\nI\'m now integrating the plan generation call. I\'m focusing on crafting the request to generate the personalized diet plan, using the user\'s profile data. This involves formulating the prompt with the details, including age, gender, weight, height, goal, and activity level. Then, I am structuring the desired response in JSON, specifying the expected output for calories, macros, daily meals, and a grocery list within a pre-defined schema.\n\n\n**Refining JSON Output Handling**\n\nI\'ve just added error handling within the API call by using a try-catch block. In the \"try\" section, I\'m now parsing the `response.text` as JSON, using it to populate the `dietPlan` state. After that, I activate the \"diet\" tab. If an error is caught during the JSON parsing (or if the API response itself is the problem), the \"catch\" block is executed, logging the error and updating the `error` state. I\'m also ensuring the `isGenerating` state is set back to false after it either succeeds or fails.\n\n\n**Implementing Profile Fields**\n\nI\'m now building the profile setup section for the dashboard. I\'m focusing on creating input fields for age, gender, weight, height, goal, and activity level. Each field is connected to the `profile` state, utilizing `useState` to manage and update the values entered by the user. I\'ve also integrated an error message display.\n\n\n**Adding Profile Data Input**\n\nI am now implementing input fields to capture user profile details. I\'ve integrated a select dropdown for gender, and numeric input fields for weight and height. These elements are being linked to the profile state using `useState` to update values based on user input. I am ensuring that the correct data types are also passed along to the `profile` object.\n\n\n**Integrating Select Components**\n\nI\'m now integrating select components to capture the user\'s \"goal\" and \"activity level\" within the profile section. I\'ve successfully connected these select fields to the `profile` state using `useState` to dynamically update the values as the user makes selections, keeping the system responsive.\n\n\n**Finalizing Generation Controls**\n\nI am now focusing on refining the save and generation controls within the diet plan component. I\'ve disabled the generation button while loading using `isGenerating`, and also integrated a loading spinner. The \"Save & Generate Diet Plan\" button now accurately reflects the state, dynamically updating text based on loading. I am also making sure that the overall structure is clean and responsive.\n\n\n**Refining UI Structure**\n\nI\'m now integrating a \"No Diet Plan\" state, rendering a placeholder message with a call to action if no plan exists yet. This involves conditionally rendering an \"empty state\" UI, and linking a button to redirect the user to the profile setup if the `dietPlan` state is empty. This empty state includes an icon, a clear message, and a call-to-action button, enhancing user experience.\n\n\n**Enhancing Daily Target Display**\n\nI am now focusing on refining the user interface to enhance the display of daily targets within the diet plan component. I\'ve integrated a visual display to present the daily target values. I\'ve also added \"Regenerate\" to match UI button style and function. I am currently evaluating potential ways to make this display more intuitive.\n\n\n\n**Improving Target Display**\n\nI am now focusing on cleaning up the visual presentation of the daily macros and calorie goals. I\'m aiming to make the data much clearer. I\'m refining the formatting of the text and potentially adjusting the layout of the macro and calorie displays for better readability.\n\n\n**Refining Meal Plan Details**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the visual enhancements for the individual meal display. I\'m incorporating a concise display of meal descriptions and caloric values for each meal, ensuring clarity. I\'ve also added styling to highlight the \"Today\'s Meal Plan\" header and improve its aesthetics. I am also making sure to iterate through each `dietPlan.meals` to display all meal data.\n\n\n"
    tool_calls {
      id: "oj1m4mz2"
      name: "multi_edit_file"
      arguments_json: "{\"Instruction\":\"Update UserDashboard.tsx to include dynamic AI Diet Generation using Gemini\",\"ReplacementChunks\":[{\"ReplacementContent\":\"import { useState } from \\\"react\\\";\\nimport { \\n  User, \\n  Utensils, \\n  Dumbbell, \\n  TrendingUp, \\n  CalendarCheck, \\n  MessageSquare, \\n  CreditCard,\\n  LogOut,\\n  Menu,\\n  X,\\n  Send,\\n  Upload,\\n  Loader2\\n} from \\\"lucide-react\\\";\\nimport { Link } from \\\"react-router-dom\\\";\\nimport { LineChart, Line, XAxis, YAxis, CartesianGrid, Tooltip, ResponsiveContainer } from \'recharts\';\\nimport { GoogleGenAI, Type } from \\\"@google/genai\\\";\",\"TargetContent\":\"import { useState } from \\\"react\\\";\\nimport { \\n  User, \\n  Utensils, \\n  Dumbbell, \\n  TrendingUp, \\n  CalendarCheck, \\n  MessageSquare, \\n  CreditCard,\\n  LogOut,\\n  Menu,\\n  X,\\n  Send,\\n  Upload\\n} from \\\"lucide-react\\\";\\nimport { Link } from \\\"react-router-dom\\\";\\nimport { LineChart, Line, XAxis, YAxis, CartesianGrid, Tooltip, ResponsiveContainer } from \'recharts\';\"},{\"ReplacementContent\":\"export default function UserDashboard() {\\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState(\\\"profile\\\");\\n  const [isSidebarOpen, setIsSidebarOpen] = useState(false);\\n\\n  const [profile, setProfile] = useState({\\n    age: 28,\\n    gender: \'Male\',\\n    weight: 85,\\n    height: 180,\\n    goal: \'Fat Loss\',\\n    activityLevel: \'Moderate\'\\n  });\\n  const [dietPlan, setDietPlan] = useState<any>(null);\\n  const [isGenerating, setIsGenerating] = useState(false);\\n  const [error, setError] = useState(\\\"\\\");\\n\\n  const generateDietPlan = async () => {\\n    setIsGenerating(true);\\n    setError(\\\"\\\");\\n    try {\\n      const ai = new GoogleGenAI({ apiKey: process.env.GEMINI_API_KEY });\\n      const response = await ai.models.generateContent({\\n        model: \\\"gemini-3-flash-preview\\\",\\n        contents: `Generate a personalized diet plan for a ${profile.age} year old ${profile.gender}, weighing ${profile.weight}kg, ${profile.height}cm tall, with a goal of ${profile.goal} and activity level ${profile.activityLevel}. Provide realistic daily calories, macros in grams, a daily meal plan, and a grocery list.`,\\n        config: {\\n          responseMimeType: \\\"application/json\\\",\\n          responseSchema: {\\n            type: Type.OBJECT,\\n            properties: {\\n              calories: { type: Type.NUMBER },\\n              macros: {\\n                type: Type.OBJECT,\\n                properties: {\\n                  protein: { type: Type.NUMBER },\\n                  carbs: { type: Type.NUMBER },\\n                  fat: { type: Type.NUMBER }\\n                },\\n                required: [\\\"protein\\\", \\\"carbs\\\", \\\"fat\\\"]\\n              },\\n              meals: {\\n                type: Type.ARRAY,\\n                items: {\\n                  type: Type.OBJECT,\\n                  properties: {\\n                    name: { type: Type.STRING },\\n                    description: { type: Type.STRING },\\n                    calories: { type: Type.NUMBER }\\n                  },\\n                  required: [\\\"name\\\", \\\"description\\\", \\\"calories\\\"]\\n                }\\n              },\\n              groceryList: {\\n                type: Type.ARRAY,\\n                items: { type: Type.STRING }\\n              }\\n            },\\n            required: [\\\"calories\\\", \\\"macros\\\", \\\"meals\\\", \\\"groceryList\\\"]\\n          }\\n        }\\n      });\\n      if (response.text) {\\n        setDietPlan(JSON.parse(response.text));\\n        setActiveTab(\\\"diet\\\");\\n      }\\n    } catch (err) {\\n      console.error(\\\"Failed to generate diet plan:\\\", err);\\n      setError(\\\"Failed to generate diet plan. Please check your API key and try again.\\\");\\n    } finally {\\n      setIsGenerating(false);\\n    }\\n  };\\n\\n  const tabs = [\",\"TargetContent\":\"export default function UserDashboard() {\\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState(\\\"profile\\\");\\n  const [isSidebarOpen, setIsSidebarOpen] = useState(false);\\n\\n  const tabs = [\"},{\"ReplacementContent\":\"      case \\\"profile\\\":\\n        return (\\n          <div className=\\\"space-y-6 max-w-2xl\\\">\\n            <div>\\n              <h2 className=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">Profile Setup</h2>\\n              <p className=\\\"text-zinc-500\\\">Update your personal information to get accurate plans.</p>\\n            </div>\\n            <div className=\\\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200 space-y-4\\\">\\n              {error && <div className=\\\"p-3 bg-red-50 text-red-600 rounded-lg text-sm\\\">{error}</div>}\\n              <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n                  <label className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700\\\">Age</label>\\n                  <input type=\\\"number\\\" value={profile.age} onChange={e => setProfile({...profile, age: Number(e.target.value)})} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none\\\" />\\n                </div>\\n                <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n                  <label className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700\\\">Gender</label>\\n                  <select value={profile.gender} onChange={e => setProfile({...profile, gender: e.target.value})} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none\\\">\\n                    <option>Male</option>\\n                    <option>Female</option>\\n                    <option>Other</option>\\n                  </select>\\n                </div>\\n                <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n                  <label className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700\\\">Weight (kg)</label>\\n                  <input type=\\\"number\\\" value={profile.weight} onChange={e => setProfile({...profile, weight: Number(e.target.value)})} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none\\\" />\\n                </div>\\n                <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n                  <label className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700\\\">Height (cm)</label>\\n                  <input type=\\\"number\\\" value={profile.height} onChange={e => setProfile({...profile, height: Number(e.target.value)})} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none\\\" />\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n              <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n                  <label className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700\\\">Goal</label>\\n                  <select value={profile.goal} onChange={e => setProfile({...profile, goal: e.target.value})} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none\\\">\\n                    <option>Fat Loss</option>\\n                    <option>Muscle Gain</option>\\n                    <option>Maintenance</option>\\n                  </select>\\n                </div>\\n                <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n                  <label className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700\\\">Activity Level</label>\\n                  <select value={profile.activityLevel} onChange={e => setProfile({...profile, activityLevel: e.target.value})} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none\\\">\\n                    <option>Sedentary</option>\\n                    <option>Lightly Active</option>\\n                    <option>Moderate</option>\\n                    <option>Very Active</option>\\n                    <option>Extra Active</option>\\n                  </select>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n              <button \\n                onClick={generateDietPlan}\\n                disabled={isGenerating}\\n                className=\\\"w-full bg-emerald-600 text-white py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2 disabled:opacity-70\\\"\\n              >\\n                {isGenerating && <Loader2 className=\\\"w-4 h-4 animate-spin\\\" />}\\n                {isGenerating ? \\\"Generating Plan...\\\" : \\\"Save & Generate Diet Plan\\\"}\\n              </button>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        );\",\"TargetContent\":\"      case \\\"profile\\\":\\n        return (\\n          <div className=\\\"space-y-6 max-w-2xl\\\">\\n            <div>\\n              <h2 className=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">Profile Setup</h2>\\n              <p className=\\\"text-zinc-500\\\">Update your personal information to get accurate plans.</p>\\n            </div>\\n            <div className=\\\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200 space-y-4\\\">\\n              <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n                  <label className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700\\\">Age</label>\\n                  <input type=\\\"number\\\" defaultValue={28} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none\\\" />\\n                </div>\\n                <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n                  <label className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700\\\">Gender</label>\\n                  <select className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none\\\">\\n                    <option>Male</option>\\n                    <option>Female</option>\\n                    <option>Other</option>\\n                  </select>\\n                </div>\\n                <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n                  <label className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700\\\">Weight (kg)</label>\\n                  <input type=\\\"number\\\" defaultValue={85} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none\\\" />\\n                </div>\\n                <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n                  <label className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700\\\">Height (cm)</label>\\n                  <input type=\\\"number\\\" defaultValue={180} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none\\\" />\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n              <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n                <label className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700\\\">Goal</label>\\n                <select className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 outline-none\\\">\\n                  <option>Fat Loss</option>\\n                  <option>Muscle Gain</option>\\n                  <option>Maintenance</option>\\n                </select>\\n              </div>\\n              <button className=\\\"w-full bg-emerald-600 text-white py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-colors\\\">\\n                Save Profile\\n              </button>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        );\"},{\"ReplacementContent\":\"      case \\\"diet\\\":\\n        if (!dietPlan) {\\n          return (\\n            <div className=\\\"space-y-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-96 text-center\\\">\\n              <div className=\\\"w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4\\\">\\n                <Utensils className=\\\"w-8 h-8\\\" />\\n              </div>\\n              <h2 className=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">No Diet Plan Yet</h2>\\n              <p className=\\\"text-zinc-500 max-w-md\\\">Complete your profile and generate your personalized AI diet plan to get started.</p>\\n              <button \\n                onClick={() => setActiveTab(\\\"profile\\\")}\\n                className=\\\"mt-4 bg-emerald-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-colors\\\"\\n              >\\n                Go to Profile\\n              </button>\\n            </div>\\n          );\\n        }\\n\\n        return (\\n          <div className=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n            <div className=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n              <div>\\n                <h2 className=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">AI Diet Generator</h2>\\n                <p className=\\\"text-zinc-500\\\">Your personalized nutrition plan based on your profile.</p>\\n              </div>\\n              <button \\n                onClick={generateDietPlan}\\n                disabled={isGenerating}\\n                className=\\\"bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 text-sm disabled:opacity-70\\\"\\n              >\\n                {isGenerating ? <Loader2 className=\\\"w-4 h-4 animate-spin\\\" /> : <Utensils className=\\\"w-4 h-4\\\" />}\\n                Regenerate\\n              </button>\\n            </div>\\n            \\n            <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\\\">\\n              <div className=\\\"md:col-span-2 space-y-6\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n                  <div>\\n                    <h3 className=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\">Daily Target</h3>\\n                    <p className=\\\"text-zinc-500\\\">Calculated for {profile.goal}</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n                    <span className=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-600\\\">{dietPlan.calories}</span>\\n                    <span className=\\\"text-zinc-500 ml-1\\\">kcal</span>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4\\\">\\n                  <div className=\\\"bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 text-center\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-1\\\">Protein</div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">{dietPlan.macros.protein}g</div>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 text-center\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-1\\\">Carbs</div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">{dietPlan.macros.carbs}g</div>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 text-center\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-1\\\">Fat</div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">{dietPlan.macros.fat}g</div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <div className=\\\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n                  <div className=\\\"p-4 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\">Today\'s Meal Plan</div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"divide-y divide-zinc-100\\\">\\n                    {dietPlan.meals.map((meal: any, idx: number) => (\\n                      <div key={idx} className=\\\"p-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors cursor-pointer\\\">\\n                        <div>\\n                          <h4 className=\\\"font-medium text-zinc-900\\\">{meal.name}</h4>\\n                          <p className=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-500\\\">{meal.description}</p>\\n                        </div>\\n                        <span className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-emerald-600\\\">{meal.calories} kcal</span>\\n                      </div>\\n                    ))}\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n\\n              <div className=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200\\\">\\n                  <h3 className=\\\"font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-4\\\">Grocery List</h3>\\n                  <ul className=\\\"space-y-3\\\">\\n                    {dietPlan.groceryList.map((item: string, idx: number) => (\\n                      <li key={idx} className=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-700\\\">\\n                        <input type=\\\"checkbox\\\" className=\\\"rounded text-emerald-600 focus:ring-emerald-500\\\" /> {item}\\n                      </li>\\n                    ))}\\n                  </ul>\\n                  <button className=\\\"w-full mt-6 text-sm text-emerald-600 font-medium hover:text-emerald-700\\\">\\n                    Export to PDF\\n                  </button>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        );\",\"TargetContent\":\"      case \\\"diet\\\":\\n        return (\\n          <div className=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n            <div>\\n              <h2 className=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">AI Diet Generator</h2>\\n              <p className=\\\"text-zinc-500\\\">Your personalized nutrition plan based on your profile.</p>\\n            </div>\\n            \\n            <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\\\">\\n              <div className=\\\"md:col-span-2 space-y-6\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n                  <div>\\n                    <h3 className=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\">Daily Target</h3>\\n                    <p className=\\\"text-zinc-500\\\">Calculated for Fat Loss</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n                    <span className=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-600\\\">2,200</span>\\n                    <span className=\\\"text-zinc-500 ml-1\\\">kcal</span>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4\\\">\\n                  <div className=\\\"bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 text-center\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-1\\\">Protein</div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">160g</div>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 text-center\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-1\\\">Carbs</div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">220g</div>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 text-center\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-1\\\">Fat</div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">70g</div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <div className=\\\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n                  <div className=\\\"p-4 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\">Today\'s Meal Plan</div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"divide-y divide-zinc-100\\\">\\n                    {[\'Breakfast\', \'Lunch\', \'Snack\', \'Dinner\'].map((meal) => (\\n                      <div key={meal} className=\\\"p-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors cursor-pointer\\\">\\n                        <div>\\n                          <h4 className=\\\"font-medium text-zinc-900\\\">{meal}</h4>\\n                          <p className=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-500\\\">Oats, Whey Protein, Berries</p>\\n                        </div>\\n                        <span className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-emerald-600\\\">450 kcal</span>\\n                      </div>\\n                    ))}\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n\\n              <div className=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200\\\">\\n                  <h3 className=\\\"font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-4\\\">Grocery List</h3>\\n                  <ul className=\\\"space-y-3\\\">\\n                    <li className=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-700\\\">\\n                      <input type=\\\"checkbox\\\" className=\\\"rounded text-emerald-600 focus:ring-emerald-500\\\" /> Chicken Breast (1kg)\\n                    </li>\\n                    <li className=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-700\\\">\\n                      <input type=\\\"checkbox\\\" className=\\\"rounded text-emerald-600 focus:ring-emerald-500\\\" /> Rolled Oats (500g)\\n                    </li>\\n                    <li className=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-700\\\">\\n                      <input type=\\\"checkbox\\\" className=\\\"rounded text-emerald-600 focus:ring-emerald-500\\\" /> Greek Yogurt (1 tub)\\n                    </li>\\n                    <li className=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-700\\\">\\n                      <input type=\\\"checkbox\\\" className=\\\"rounded text-emerald-600 focus:ring-emerald-500\\\" /> Mixed Berries (Frozen)\\n                    </li>\\n                  </ul>\\n                  <button className=\\\"w-full mt-6 text-sm text-emerald-600 font-medium hover:text-emerald-700\\\">\\n                    Export to PDF\\n                  </button>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        );\"}],\"TargetFile\":\"/src/pages/UserDashboard.tsx\",\"toolSummary\":\"Update UserDashboard with Dynamic AI Diet Generator\"}"
      thought_signature: ""
    }
