  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Defining the Objective**\n\nI\'m currently focused on the overarching goal: integrating a \"Coach Panel\" into the application, drawing directly from the original PDF\'s specifications. Right now, I\'m specifically examining the \"Client Management\" section within that document to ensure I grasp the necessary features related to assigned clients and progress reports. I\'m aiming for a comprehensive understanding.\n\n\n**Outlining Key Features**\n\nI\'ve moved on to fleshing out the core functionality. I\'m focusing on features such as creating and editing diet plans with custom macros and meals. Next, I\'m working to make a workout plan builder and a client messaging system with chat, voice notes, and file sharing features. I\'m striving to ensure each component addresses the specifications, like the weekly check-ins.\n\n\n**Visualizing the Structure**\n\nNow I\'m diving into the UI elements. I\'m planning out how the Coach Panel will look, specifically focusing on the structure within the selected client context. I\'m envisioning tabs for client lists, diet plans, workout routines, and messages. The goal is to use Tailwind CSS to achieve a consistent yet distinct visual identity with an `indigo` theme for the coach panel. I\'m mapping out the specifics of each tab, like client cards in the \"Clients\" tab and form inputs in \"Diet\" plan.\n\n\n**Implementing the Interface**\n\nI\'m now in the thick of implementation! I\'ve kicked off development by crafting `CoachDashboard.tsx` and updating routing. I\'ve wired in a basic dashboard structure, complete with Lucide icons for navigation, and I\'ve even set up a state for tab management. My next step involves fleshing out each tab\'s unique content.\n\n\n"
    tool_calls {
      id: "0hyn0rke"
      name: "create_file"
      arguments_json: "{\"Content\":\"import { useState } from \\\"react\\\";\\nimport { \\n  Users, \\n  Utensils, \\n  Dumbbell, \\n  MessageSquare, \\n  LogOut,\\n  Menu,\\n  X,\\n  Search,\\n  Plus,\\n  ChevronRight,\\n  Send,\\n  Paperclip,\\n  Mic,\\n  CheckCircle2\\n} from \\\"lucide-react\\\";\\nimport { Link } from \\\"react-router-dom\\\";\\n\\nexport default function CoachDashboard() {\\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState(\\\"clients\\\");\\n  const [isSidebarOpen, setIsSidebarOpen] = useState(false);\\n  const [selectedClient, setSelectedClient] = useState(\\\"Rahul Sharma\\\");\\n\\n  const tabs = [\\n    { id: \\\"clients\\\", label: \\\"Client Management\\\", icon: Users },\\n    { id: \\\"diet\\\", label: \\\"Diet Plan Editor\\\", icon: Utensils },\\n    { id: \\\"workout\\\", label: \\\"Workout Builder\\\", icon: Dumbbell },\\n    { id: \\\"messages\\\", label: \\\"Client Messaging\\\", icon: MessageSquare },\\n  ];\\n\\n  const renderContent = () => {\\n    switch (activeTab) {\\n      case \\\"clients\\\":\\n        return (\\n          <div className=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n            <div className=\\\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-4\\\">\\n              <div>\\n                <h2 className=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">Client Management</h2>\\n                <p className=\\\"text-zinc-500\\\">Monitor progress and review weekly check-ins.</p>\\n              </div>\\n              <div className=\\\"relative w-full sm:w-64\\\">\\n                <Search className=\\\"w-4 h-4 absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-zinc-400\\\" />\\n                <input \\n                  type=\\\"text\\\" \\n                  placeholder=\\\"Search clients...\\\" \\n                  className=\\\"w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-2 border border-zinc-200 rounded-lg text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none\\\"\\n                />\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\\\">\\n              <div className=\\\"lg:col-span-2 space-y-4\\\">\\n                {[\\n                  { name: \\\"Rahul Sharma\\\", goal: \\\"Fat Loss\\\", status: \\\"Checked in today\\\", weight: \\\"82.1 kg\\\", trend: \\\"-0.8 kg\\\" },\\n                  { name: \\\"Neha Singh\\\", goal: \\\"Fat Loss\\\", status: \\\"Check-in pending\\\", weight: \\\"65.4 kg\\\", trend: \\\"-0.2 kg\\\" },\\n                  { name: \\\"Arjun Patel\\\", goal: \\\"Muscle Gain\\\", status: \\\"Checked in yesterday\\\", weight: \\\"74.5 kg\\\", trend: \\\"+0.5 kg\\\" },\\n                ].map((client, i) => (\\n                  <div key={i} className=\\\"bg-white p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-4 hover:border-indigo-200 transition-colors cursor-pointer\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n                      <div className=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-700 font-bold text-lg\\\">\\n                        {client.name.charAt(0)}\\n                      </div>\\n                      <div>\\n                        <h3 className=\\\"font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\">{client.name}</h3>\\n                        <p className=\\\"text-sm text-zinc-500\\\">{client.goal} \342\200\242 {client.status}</p>\\n                      </div>\\n                    </div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"flex items-center gap-6 w-full sm:w-auto justify-between sm:justify-end\\\">\\n                      <div className=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n                        <p className=\\\"font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\">{client.weight}</p>\\n                        <p className={`text-xs font-medium ${client.trend.startsWith(\'-\') && client.goal === \'Fat Loss\' ? \'text-emerald-600\' : \'text-zinc-500\'}`}>\\n                          {client.trend} this week\\n                        </p>\\n                      </div>\\n                      <ChevronRight className=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-zinc-400\\\" />\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                ))}\\n              </div>\\n\\n              <div className=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200\\\">\\n                  <h3 className=\\\"font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-4\\\">Recent Check-ins</h3>\\n                  <div className=\\\"space-y-4\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"p-3 bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl border border-indigo-100\\\">\\n                      <div className=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2\\\">\\n                        <span className=\\\"font-medium text-indigo-900 text-sm\\\">Rahul Sharma</span>\\n                        <span className=\\\"text-xs text-indigo-600\\\">2h ago</span>\\n                      </div>\\n                      <p className=\\\"text-xs text-indigo-800 mb-2\\\">\\\"Energy levels were great this week, but struggled with sleep on Thursday.\\\"</p>\\n                      <button className=\\\"text-xs font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700 flex items-center gap-1\\\">\\n                        Review Check-in <ChevronRight className=\\\"w-3 h-3\\\" />\\n                      </button>\\n                    </div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"p-3 bg-zinc-50 rounded-xl border border-zinc-100\\\">\\n                      <div className=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2\\\">\\n                        <span className=\\\"font-medium text-zinc-900 text-sm\\\">Arjun Patel</span>\\n                        <span className=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-500\\\">1d ago</span>\\n                      </div>\\n                      <p className=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-600 mb-2\\\">\\\"Hit a new PR on bench press! Weight is slowly creeping up.\\\"</p>\\n                      <button className=\\\"text-xs font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700 flex items-center gap-1\\\">\\n                        Review Check-in <ChevronRight className=\\\"w-3 h-3\\\" />\\n                      </button>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        );\\n      case \\\"diet\\\":\\n        return (\\n          <div className=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n            <div className=\\\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-4\\\">\\n              <div>\\n                <h2 className=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">Diet Plan Editor</h2>\\n                <p className=\\\"text-zinc-500\\\">Create and modify custom diet plans for clients.</p>\\n              </div>\\n              <select \\n                value={selectedClient}\\n                onChange={(e) => setSelectedClient(e.target.value)}\\n                className=\\\"p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none bg-white text-sm font-medium\\\"\\n              >\\n                <option>Rahul Sharma</option>\\n                <option>Neha Singh</option>\\n                <option>Arjun Patel</option>\\n              </select>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\\\">\\n              <div className=\\\"lg:col-span-2 space-y-6\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200\\\">\\n                  <div className=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-6\\\">\\n                    <h3 className=\\\"font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\">Macro Targets</h3>\\n                    <button className=\\\"text-sm text-indigo-600 font-medium hover:text-indigo-700\\\">Auto-calculate</button>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"space-y-1\\\">\\n                      <label className=\\\"text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Calories</label>\\n                      <input type=\\\"number\\\" defaultValue={2200} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\" />\\n                    </div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"space-y-1\\\">\\n                      <label className=\\\"text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Protein (g)</label>\\n                      <input type=\\\"number\\\" defaultValue={160} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\" />\\n                    </div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"space-y-1\\\">\\n                      <label className=\\\"text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Carbs (g)</label>\\n                      <input type=\\\"number\\\" defaultValue={220} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\" />\\n                    </div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"space-y-1\\\">\\n                      <label className=\\\"text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Fat (g)</label>\\n                      <input type=\\\"number\\\" defaultValue={70} className=\\\"w-full p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\" />\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <div className=\\\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n                  <div className=\\\"p-4 border-b border-zinc-200 flex justify-between items-center bg-zinc-50\\\">\\n                    <h3 className=\\\"font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\">Meals</h3>\\n                    <button className=\\\"text-sm bg-white border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-zinc-50 flex items-center gap-1\\\">\\n                      <Plus className=\\\"w-4 h-4\\\" /> Add Meal\\n                    </button>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"divide-y divide-zinc-100\\\">\\n                    {[\\n                      { name: \\\"Breakfast\\\", items: \\\"Oats (50g), Whey Protein (1 scoop), Almonds (15g)\\\", cals: 420 },\\n                      { name: \\\"Lunch\\\", items: \\\"Chicken Breast (150g), White Rice (100g), Broccoli\\\", cals: 550 },\\n                      { name: \\\"Pre-workout Snack\\\", items: \\\"Banana (1 medium), Rice Cakes (2)\\\", cals: 180 },\\n                    ].map((meal, i) => (\\n                      <div key={i} className=\\\"p-4 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors\\\">\\n                        <div className=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2\\\">\\n                          <input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue={meal.name} className=\\\"font-medium text-zinc-900 bg-transparent border-none p-0 focus:ring-0 outline-none\\\" />\\n                          <span className=\\\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-500\\\">{meal.cals} kcal</span>\\n                        </div>\\n                        <textarea \\n                          defaultValue={meal.items} \\n                          rows={2}\\n                          className=\\\"w-full text-sm text-zinc-600 bg-transparent border border-transparent hover:border-zinc-200 focus:border-indigo-500 rounded p-1 outline-none resize-none\\\"\\n                        />\\n                      </div>\\n                    ))}\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                \\n                <button className=\\\"w-full bg-indigo-600 text-white py-2.5 rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors\\\">\\n                  Save & Publish Diet Plan\\n                </button>\\n              </div>\\n\\n              <div className=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"bg-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-indigo-100\\\">\\n                  <h3 className=\\\"font-semibold text-indigo-900 mb-2\\\">Client Context</h3>\\n                  <ul className=\\\"space-y-2 text-sm text-indigo-800\\\">\\n                    <li><span className=\\\"font-medium\\\">Goal:</span> Fat Loss</li>\\n                    <li><span className=\\\"font-medium\\\">Current Weight:</span> 82.1 kg</li>\\n                    <li><span className=\\\"font-medium\\\">Allergies:</span> None</li>\\n                    <li><span className=\\\"font-medium\\\">Preferences:</span> High protein, easy to cook</li>\\n                  </ul>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        );\\n      case \\\"workout\\\":\\n        return (\\n          <div className=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n            <div className=\\\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-4\\\">\\n              <div>\\n                <h2 className=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900\\\">Workout Builder</h2>\\n                <p className=\\\"text-zinc-500\\\">Design custom training routines.</p>\\n              </div>\\n              <select \\n                value={selectedClient}\\n                onChange={(e) => setSelectedClient(e.target.value)}\\n                className=\\\"p-2 border border-zinc-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none bg-white text-sm font-medium\\\"\\n              >\\n                <option>Rahul Sharma</option>\\n                <option>Neha Singh</option>\\n                <option>Arjun Patel</option>\\n              </select>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <div className=\\\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n              <div className=\\\"p-4 border-b border-zinc-200 flex justify-between items-center bg-zinc-50\\\">\\n                <h3 className=\\\"font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\">Training Split</h3>\\n                <button className=\\\"text-sm bg-white border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-zinc-50 flex items-center gap-1\\\">\\n                  <Plus className=\\\"w-4 h-4\\\" /> Add Day\\n                </button>\\n              </div>\\n              \\n              <div className=\\\"p-6 space-y-6\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"border border-zinc-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\">\\n                  <div className=\\\"bg-zinc-50 p-3 border-b border-zinc-200 flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n                    <input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"Day 1: Push (Chest, Shoulders, Triceps)\\\" className=\\\"font-semibold text-zinc-900 bg-transparent border-none p-0 focus:ring-0 outline-none w-full max-w-md\\\" />\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"p-0\\\">\\n                    <table className=\\\"w-full text-sm text-left\\\">\\n                      <thead className=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-500 uppercase bg-white border-b border-zinc-100\\\">\\n                        <tr>\\n                          <th className=\\\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\\\">Exercise</th>\\n                          <th className=\\\"px-4 py-3 font-medium w-24\\\">Sets</th>\\n                          <th className=\\\"px-4 py-3 font-medium w-32\\\">Reps</th>\\n                          <th className=\\\"px-4 py-3 font-medium w-32\\\">Rest</th>\\n                        </tr>\\n                      </thead>\\n                      <tbody className=\\\"divide-y divide-zinc-100\\\">\\n                        <tr>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"Barbell Bench Press\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"3\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"8-10\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"90s\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                        </tr>\\n                        <tr>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"Incline Dumbbell Press\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"3\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"10-12\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"60s\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                        </tr>\\n                        <tr>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"Lateral Raises\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"4\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"15\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                          <td className=\\\"px-4 py-3\\\"><input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"45s\\\" className=\\\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none\\\" /></td>\\n                        </tr>\\n                      </tbody>\\n                    </table>\\n                    <div className=\\\"p-3 bg-zinc-50 border-t border-zinc-100\\\">\\n                      <button className=\\\"text-sm text-indigo-600 font-medium hover:text-indigo-700 flex items-center gap-1\\\">\\n                        <Plus className=\\\"w-4 h-4\\\" /> Add Exercise\\n                      </button>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <div className=\\\"border border-zinc-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\\\">\\n                  <div className=\\\"bg-zinc-50 p-3 border-b border-zinc-200 flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n                    <input type=\\\"text\\\" defaultValue=\\\"Day 2: Pull (Back, Biceps)\\\" className=\\\"font-semibold text-zinc-900 bg-transparent border-none p-0 focus:ring-0 outline-none w-full max-w-md\\\" />\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"p-3 bg-white text-sm text-zinc-500 text-center\\\">\\n                    2 exercises added. Click to expand.\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            \\n            <div className=\\\"flex justify-end\\\">\\n              <button className=\\\"bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors\\\">\\n                Save Workout Plan\\n              </button>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        );\\n      case \\\"messages\\\":\\n        return (\\n          <div className=\\\"h-[calc(100vh-8rem)] flex bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-zinc-200 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n            {/* Chat Sidebar */}\\n            <div className=\\\"w-1/3 border-r border-zinc-200 hidden md:flex flex-col bg-zinc-50\\\">\\n              <div className=\\\"p-4 border-b border-zinc-200\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"relative\\\">\\n                  <Search className=\\\"w-4 h-4 absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-zinc-400\\\" />\\n                  <input \\n                    type=\\\"text\\\" \\n                    placeholder=\\\"Search messages...\\\" \\n                    className=\\\"w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-2 bg-white border border-zinc-200 rounded-lg text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none\\\"\\n                  />\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n              <div className=\\\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto\\\">\\n                {[\\n                  { name: \\\"Rahul Sharma\\\", msg: \\\"Awesome, thanks Alex! The workouts...\\\", time: \\\"10:42 AM\\\", unread: false },\\n                  { name: \\\"Neha Singh\\\", msg: \\\"Can I swap chicken for fish today?\\\", time: \\\"Yesterday\\\", unread: true },\\n                  { name: \\\"Arjun Patel\\\", msg: \\\"Check-in submitted!\\\", time: \\\"Yesterday\\\", unread: false },\\n                ].map((chat, i) => (\\n                  <div key={i} className={`p-4 border-b border-zinc-100 cursor-pointer hover:bg-zinc-100 transition-colors ${i === 0 ? \'bg-white border-l-4 border-l-indigo-500\' : \'\'}`}>\\n                    <div className=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-1\\\">\\n                      <h4 className={`text-sm ${chat.unread ? \'font-bold text-zinc-900\' : \'font-medium text-zinc-700\'}`}>{chat.name}</h4>\\n                      <span className=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-400\\\">{chat.time}</span>\\n                    </div>\\n                    <div className=\\\"flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n                      <p className={`text-xs truncate pr-4 ${chat.unread ? \'font-medium text-zinc-900\' : \'text-zinc-500\'}`}>{chat.msg}</p>\\n                      {chat.unread && <span className=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0\\\"></span>}\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                ))}\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            {/* Chat Area */}\\n            <div className=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n              <div className=\\\"p-4 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n                  <div className=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-700 font-bold\\\">\\n                    R\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div>\\n                    <h3 className=\\\"font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\">Rahul Sharma</h3>\\n                    <p className=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-500\\\">Goal: Fat Loss</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <button className=\\\"text-sm text-indigo-600 font-medium hover:text-indigo-700 bg-indigo-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg\\\">\\n                  View Profile\\n                </button>\\n              </div>\\n              \\n              <div className=\\\"flex-1 p-4 overflow-y-auto space-y-4 bg-zinc-50/50\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"flex justify-center\\\">\\n                  <span className=\\\"text-xs text-zinc-400 bg-zinc-100 px-2 py-1 rounded-full\\\">Today</span>\\n                </div>\\n                <div className=\\\"flex gap-3 max-w-[80%] ml-auto flex-row-reverse\\\">\\n                  <div className=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0\\\">\\n                    C\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"bg-indigo-600 p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none shadow-sm text-sm text-white\\\">\\n                    Hey! I reviewed your check-in. Great progress on the weight loss! Let\'s bump up your carbs slightly on training days. I\'ve updated your diet plan.\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <div className=\\\"flex gap-3 max-w-[80%]\\\">\\n                  <div className=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-zinc-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-700 font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0\\\">\\n                    R\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div className=\\\"bg-white p-3 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none shadow-sm border border-zinc-100 text-sm text-zinc-800\\\">\\n                    Awesome, thanks Alex! The workouts have been feeling great too.\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n\\n              <div className=\\\"p-4 border-t border-zinc-200 bg-white\\\">\\n                <div className=\\\"flex gap-2 items-center\\\">\\n                  <button className=\\\"p-2 text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-600 transition-colors\\\">\\n                    <Paperclip className=\\\"w-5 h-5\\\" />\\n                  </button>\\n                  <button className=\\\"p-2 text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-600 transition-colors\\\">\\n                    <Mic className=\\\"w-5 h-5\\\" />\\n                  </button>\\n                  <input \\n                    type=\\\"text\\\" \\n                    placeholder=\\\"Type your message...\\\" \\n                    className=\\\"flex-1 p-2 bg-zinc-100 border-transparent rounded-full focus:bg-white focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none px-4 text-sm\\\"\\n                  />\\n                  <button className=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors flex-shrink-0\\\">\\n                    <Send className=\\\"w-4 h-4\\\" />\\n                  </button>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        );\\n      default:\\n        return null;\\n    }\\n  };\\n\\n  return (\\n    <div className=\\\"min-h-screen bg-zinc-50 flex\\\">\\n      {/* Mobile Sidebar Overlay */}\\n      {isSidebarOpen && (\\n        <div \\n          className=\\\"fixed inset-0 bg-black/20 z-20 md:hidden\\\"\\n          onClick={() => setIsSidebarOpen(false)}\\n        />\\n      )}\\n\\n      {/* Sidebar */}\\n      <aside className={`\\n        fixed inset-y-0 left-0 z-30 w-64 bg-white border-r border-zinc-200 transform transition-transform duration-200 ease-in-out md:relative md:translate-x-0\\n        ${isSidebarOpen ? \'translate-x-0\' : \'-translate-x-full\'}\\n      `}>\\n        <div className=\\\"p-6 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n          <Link to=\\\"/\\\" className=\\\"text-2xl font-extrabold text-zinc-900 tracking-tight\\\">FitByus</Link>\\n          <button className=\\\"md:hidden\\\" onClick={() => setIsSidebarOpen(false)}>\\n            <X className=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-zinc-500\\\" />\\n          </button>\\n        </div>\\n        \\n        <div className=\\\"px-4 pb-6\\\">\\n          <div className=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl mb-6 border border-indigo-100\\\">\\n            <div className=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold\\\">\\n              C\\n            </div>\\n            <div>\\n              <p className=\\\"text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-900\\\">Coach Alex</p>\\n              <p className=\\\"text-xs text-indigo-600 font-medium\\\">Head Coach</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <nav className=\\\"space-y-1\\\">\\n            {tabs.map((tab) => {\\n              const Icon = tab.icon;\\n              const isActive = activeTab === tab.id;\\n              return (\\n                <button\\n                  key={tab.id}\\n                  onClick={() => {\\n                    setActiveTab(tab.id);\\n                    setIsSidebarOpen(false);\\n                  }}\\n                  className={`w-full flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors ${\\n                    isActive \\n                      ? \\\"bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700\\\" \\n                      : \\\"text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 hover:text-zinc-900\\\"\\n                  }`}\\n                >\\n                  <Icon className={`w-5 h-5 ${isActive ? \\\"text-indigo-600\\\" : \\\"text-zinc-400\\\"}`} />\\n                  {tab.label}\\n                </button>\\n              );\\n            })}\\n          </nav>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div className=\\\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-4 border-t border-zinc-100\\\">\\n          <Link to=\\\"/\\\" className=\\\"w-full flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 hover:text-zinc-900 transition-colors\\\">\\n            <LogOut className=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-zinc-400\\\" />\\n            Sign Out\\n          </Link>\\n        </div>\\n      </aside>\\n\\n      {/* Main Content */}\\n      <main className=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col min-w-0 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <header className=\\\"bg-white border-b border-zinc-200 p-4 flex items-center md:hidden\\\">\\n          <button onClick={() => setIsSidebarOpen(true)} className=\\\"p-2 -ml-2 text-zinc-600\\\">\\n            <Menu className=\\\"w-6 h-6\\\" />\\n          </button>\\n          <span className=\\\"font-bold text-lg ml-2\\\">Coach Panel</span>\\n        </header>\\n        <div className=\\\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4 md:p-8\\\">\\n          {renderContent()}\\n        </div>\\n      </main>\\n    </div>\\n  );\\n}\\n\",\"Overwrite\":false,\"TargetFile\":\"/src/pages/CoachDashboard.tsx\",\"toolSummary\":\"Create Coach Dashboard\"}"
