    web_document {
      document_id: "https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/"
      url: "https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/"
      title: "FitByUs | Online Fitness Coaching & Transformation Programs"
      timestamp {
        seconds: 1773518070
        nanos: 140399019
      }
      chunks {
        markdown_chunk {
          text: "[About Us](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/about)\n[Programs](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/#programs)\n[Pricing](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/#pricing)\n[Transformations](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/#transformations)\n[Calculators](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/calc)\n[Blogs](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/blogs)"
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 1
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Fitness that\'s built\302\240by us, for you!"
          }
          text: "Personalized workouts, smart nutrition plans and real coaching support \342\200\224 all under one brand, Fit By Us.\nPersonalized workouts, smart nutrition plans and real coaching support \342\200\224 all under one brand, Fit By Us.\n- Custom workout & diet plans.\n- Progress tracking & accountability.\n- For fat loss, muscle gain & lifestyle change."
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 2
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Fitness that\'s built\302\240by us, for you!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Why do most people\302\240fail in fitness?"
          }
          text: "Because they try to do it alone. Random workouts, random diets, no plan and no support.Fit By Us fixes that with structured training, guidance and accountability."
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 3
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Fitness that\'s built\302\240by us, for you!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Why do most people\302\240fail in fitness?"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "The Problem"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "How FitByUs Helps"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "How FitByus\302\240Works?"
          }
          text: "### The Problem\n- \342\234\223I don\342\200\231t know what workout to follow.\n- \342\234\223I start a diet and quit after a few days.\n- \342\234\223No one tracks my progress or keeps me accountable.\n- \342\234\223I don\342\200\231t see real, visible changes in my body.\n\n### How FitByUs Helps\n- \342\234\223Clear, goal-based workout plans tailored to your body.\n- \342\234\223Simple, Indian-friendly diet plans you can actually follow.\n- \342\234\223Weekly check-ins, progress tracking, and real accountability.\n- \342\234\223Visible body transformation with before\342\200\223after tracking.\n\n### How FitByus\302\240Works?\nThree simple steps to start your fitness transformation,"
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 4
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Fitness that\'s built\302\240by us, for you!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Tell Us Your Goal"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Everything you need to transform!"
          }
          text: "## Tell Us Your Goal\nChoose your objective\342\200\224fat loss, muscle gain, or a lifestyle reset. Answer a few quick questions so we understand your needs and starting point.\n\n## Everything you need to transform!\nFitByUs gives you all the tools in one system."
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 5
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Fitness that\'s built\302\240by us, for you!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Everything you need to transform!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Personalized Workout Plans"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Smart Nutrition Guidance"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Coach Support & Accountability"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Progress Tracking"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Flexible Around Your Life"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Community & Challenges"
          }
          text: "### Personalized Workout Plans\nGym or home-based routines tailored to your level and equipment.\n\n### Smart Nutrition Guidance\nHigh-protein Indian meals, simple recipes and structured diet phases.\n\n### Coach Support & Accountability\nHuman guidance so you don\'t fall off when motivation drops.\n\n### Progress Tracking\nTrack weight, measurements and progress photos inside the system.\n\n### Flexible Around Your Life\nPlans that adjust around job, college or night shifts.\n\n### Community & Challenges\nJoin challenges, groups and leaderboards for extra push."
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 6
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Fitness that\'s built\302\240by us, for you!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "One Platform,Multiple Goals"
          }
          text: "Real programs for real people \342\200\224 not just bodybuilders."
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 7
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Fitness that\'s built\302\240by us, for you!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "One Platform,Multiple Goals"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Fat Loss Program"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Lean Muscle Program"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Beginner Reset Program"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Women\'s Toning Program"
          }
          text: "### Fat Loss Program\nBurn fat, tighten up and feel lighter with structured training and diet.\n\n### Lean Muscle Program\nBuild quality muscle while keeping body fat under control.\n\n### Beginner Reset Program\nStart again after a long gap with safe, simple and progressive workouts.\n\n### Women\'s Toning Program\nFocus on arms, waist, thighs and glutes with intelligent programming."
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 8
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Fitness that\'s built\302\240by us, for you!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Simple Plans, Real Value"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Compare Coaching\302\240Plans"
          }
          text: "## Simple Plans, Real Value\nChoose the level of coaching and accountability that fits your fitness goals.\n- Goal-based workout structure\n- Basic nutrition guidelines\n- Email-based support\n- Custom workout & diet plan\n- Weekly progress check-ins\n- Body transformation tracking\n- WhatsApp support\n- Everything in Pro\n- 1-on-1 dedicated coach\n- Plan updates every 2 weeks\n- Priority support & guidance\nLimited onboarding slots available for Premium Coaching to ensure quality guidance.\n\n## Compare Coaching\302\240Plans\nA clear breakdown of features across all Fit By Us coaching tiers.\nWorkout Plan\nCustom Diet Plan\nWeekly Check-ins\nDaily WhatsApp Support\n1-on-1 Video Calls\nHabit & Lifestyle Coaching\nMax Clients Per Coach\nSupport Priority"
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 9
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Fitness that\'s built\302\240by us, for you!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Compare Coaching\302\240Plans"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Starter"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Pro"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Premium Coaching"
          }
          text: "### Starter\n\342\234\224\n\342\234\225\n\342\234\225\n\342\234\225\n\342\234\225\n\342\234\225\nHigh\nStandard\n\n### Pro\n\342\234\224\n\342\234\224\n\342\234\224\n\342\234\224\n\342\234\225\n\342\234\225\nMedium\nHigh\n\n### Premium Coaching\n\342\234\224\n\342\234\224\n\342\234\224\n\342\234\224\n\342\234\224\n\342\234\224\nVery Low\nPriority"
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 10
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Fitness that\'s built\302\240by us, for you!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Real people,\302\240Real results"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Join FitByUs\302\240on the app!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Frequently asked\302\240questions!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Ready to rebuild your best self with FitByus?"
          }
          text: "## Real people,\302\240Real results\nThese are the kind of transformations FitByus is built for.\n-8 kg in 12 weeks\n+5 kg lean muscle in 4 months\n-6 kg & improved stamina in 10 weeks\n\n## Join FitByUs\302\240on the app!\nEverything you need to stay consistent, accountable, and on track \342\200\224 right from your phone.\n- Live & recorded workout sessions\n- Personal progress & habit tracking\n- Diet plans and trainer guidance\n- Support & check-ins in one place\nApp Launching Soon - Join Now and be the first to get access\n\n## Frequently asked\302\240questions!\nYes. We build beginner-friendly plans and guide you step by step so you never feel lost.\nNo. You can choose home-only, gym-only, or hybrid workouts when you start.\nIn Pro and Premium, your nutrition is personalized to your preferences and lifestyle.\nThrough WhatsApp, check-ins and calls depending on the plan you choose.\n\n## Ready to rebuild your best self with FitByus?\nGive yourself 12 weeks of focused coaching and see what you\'re truly capable of.\nNo crash diets. No random workouts. Just honest coaching and consistency.\n[Chat with us](https://wa.me/916261763612?text=Hi%20I%20am%20interested%20in%20FitByUs%20program)"
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 11
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Fitness that\'s built\302\240by us, for you!"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Ready to rebuild your best self with FitByus?"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Links"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Contact Us"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Join Us"
          }
          text: "### Links\n- [Home](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/)\n- [About Us](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/about)\n- [Programs](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/#programs)\n- [Pricing](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/#pricing)\n- [Transformations](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/#transformations)\n- [Calculators](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/calc)\n- [Blogs](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/blogs)\n[Home](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/)\n[About Us](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/about)\n[Programs](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/#programs)\n[Pricing](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/#pricing)\n[Transformations](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/#transformations)\n[Calculators](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/calc)\n[Blogs](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/blogs)\n\n### Contact Us\nOnline Fitness Coaching \342\200\242 India & NRI Clients\n\360\237\223\247 \302\240 [support@fitbyus.com](mailto:support@fitbyus.com)\n\360\237\223\236 \302\240 [+91 99 99 99 99 99](tel:+919999999999)\n\n### Join Us\n- [Terms and Conitions](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/terms)\n- [Privacy Policy](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/privacy-policy)\n[Terms and Conitions](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/terms)\n[Privacy Policy](https://fit-byus-website.vercel.app/privacy-policy)\n[\302\251 2026 FitByUs. All rights reserved.](https://www.anonymouslabtechnologies.com/)"
        }
      }
      summary: "Personalized fitness coaching, workout plans, and nutrition guidance to help you transform sustainably."
    }
