  planner_response {
    response: "I\'ve completed the implementation of the dark theme across the entire application to match the reference website you provided. \n\nHere\'s a summary of all the updates made to fulfill your requests:\n\n1. **Consistent Dark Theme Applied:**\n   - **Coach Dashboard:** Fully updated to the dark theme (`#09090b` background, `zinc-900` cards, and the signature yellow brand color `#f9c126`). The Client Management, Diet Plan Editor, Workout Builder, and Messages tabs all now match the new aesthetic.\n   - **Admin Dashboard & Landing Page:** I also went ahead and updated the Admin Dashboard and the Landing page to use the same dark theme so that the entire application feels cohesive and professional.\n\n2. **Component-Based File Structure:**\n   - The codebase has been modularized. All user dashboard features are now split into their own separate components inside `src/components/user/` (e.g., `ProfileSetup.tsx`, `AIDietGenerator.tsx`, `PersonalDietPlan.tsx`, etc.).\n\n3. **AI Diet Generator:**\n   - The AI Diet Generator now takes in all the requested inputs (Age, Weight, Height, Gender, Goal, Activity Level, and Diet Preference like Vegan/Vegetarian/Non-veg).\n   - It uses the Gemini API to compile these inputs and generate a customized diet plan when the user clicks the generate button.\n\n4. **Profile Setup Simplified:**\n   - The profile section has been streamlined to only ask for basic details (Name, Email, Phone Number, and Password Change).\n\n5. **Personal Diet Plan Block:**\n   - Added a dedicated \"Personal Diet Plan\" section in the User Dashboard where premium users can view the custom plans pushed to them by their assigned coach.\n   - The Coach Dashboard has the corresponding \"Diet Plan Editor\" to create and assign these plans.\n\nThe application is now fully functional with the new structure and the sleek dark theme. Let me know if you\'d like to tweak any specific styles or add more functionality!"
    thinking: "**Confirming Complete Development**\n\nEverything is running smoothly! I\'ve successfully implemented the simplified profile setup, dynamic AI diet generator with Gemini integration (considering factors like age, weight, and goals), and the coach panel. All user requests have been addressed, and I\'m ready for the next challenge.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I\'ve completed the implementation of the dark theme across the entire application to match the reference website you provided. \n\nHere\'s a summary of all the updates made to fulfill your requests:\n\n1. **Consistent Dark Theme Applied:**\n   - **Coach Dashboard:** Fully updated to the dark theme (`#09090b` background, `zinc-900` cards, and the signature yellow brand color `#f9c126`). The Client Management, Diet Plan Editor, Workout Builder, and Messages tabs all now match the new aesthetic.\n   - **Admin Dashboard & Landing Page:** I also went ahead and updated the Admin Dashboard and the Landing page to use the same dark theme so that the entire application feels cohesive and professional.\n\n2. **Component-Based File Structure:**\n   - The codebase has been modularized. All user dashboard features are now split into their own separate components inside `src/components/user/` (e.g., `ProfileSetup.tsx`, `AIDietGenerator.tsx`, `PersonalDietPlan.tsx`, etc.).\n\n3. **AI Diet Generator:**\n   - The AI Diet Generator now takes in all the requested inputs (Age, Weight, Height, Gender, Goal, Activity Level, and Diet Preference like Vegan/Vegetarian/Non-veg).\n   - It uses the Gemini API to compile these inputs and generate a customized diet plan when the user clicks the generate button.\n\n4. **Profile Setup Simplified:**\n   - The profile section has been streamlined to only ask for basic details (Name, Email, Phone Number, and Password Change).\n\n5. **Personal Diet Plan Block:**\n   - Added a dedicated \"Personal Diet Plan\" section in the User Dashboard where premium users can view the custom plans pushed to them by their assigned coach.\n   - The Coach Dashboard has the corresponding \"Diet Plan Editor\" to create and assign these plans.\n\nThe application is now fully functional with the new structure and the sleek dark theme. Let me know if you\'d like to tweak any specific styles or add more functionality!"
